{"tid":838613,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"英男陰莖被炸斷 血小板讓他長回近4公分！","createTime":"2018-09-27T09:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T13:29:21.000Z","uid":150609,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"95c5e6a44e19ed81e237547ebdbdda7535d48273","tid":838613,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"英男軍中服役陰莖被炸斷 神奇療法讓他長回近4公分！<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《太陽報》報導，舒維（Robert Schiewy）在1998年於軍中服役時，因為一次爆炸，使得他的生殖器受到傷害，不得不切斷2英寸（約5公分）下來，除了生理上的痛楚，這也一度讓他自尊心受傷。就在5年前，他發現一種名為「P-Shot」的新治療方法，醫生會將患者的血液轉換成富含血小板的血漿，再將其注入患者的生殖器，讓生殖器增加血流量並讓組織活化再生長。<br />\n<br />\n舒維花了1200英鎊（約48000新台幣）進行「P-Shot」手術，身體變得更強壯，生殖器也如願長了1.5英寸，找回自信，而且交到女朋友，性生活也非常美滿。<br />\n<br />\n替舒維做這這項治療的醫師拉哈尼（Shirin Lakhani）表示，「P-Shot」這個療程會在3周後開始見效，大約3個月左右就可以結束療程，幫助男性重展雄風。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n血小板注入jj可以活化生長 大Jer不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/170634_6c79762efdebb0360d4e9cca4e23f629.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F170634_6c79762efdebb0360d4e9cca4e23f629.gif&h=0c794367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/170436_db13da7f355078bfd12e2778ca379750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F170436_db13da7f355078bfd12e2778ca379750.jpg&h=a25e7910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd543d846dfcbf445e35751e7403af0bcbb03b52","tid":838613,"uid":3480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"玉莖重生"},{"pid":"e1e4a80e4b5e3a09028e7ac487d3fc843005b68e","tid":838613,"uid":31254,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/170842_456f30354abeea560b2be20577074a64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.e